title: Yeomen.ai - Elevate your game!
description:
Talk as part of the MUD Day CLS: autonomous worlds, onchain games, and non-financial applications.

Web3 games bring about possibilities for autonomous worlds that traditional games are not able to offer. Yeomen.ai makes the on-chain data available to the masses in simple dashboards. Yeomen.ai also offers on-chain extension of autonomous worlds to automate and transform game play.
